Firefighters and emergency services are on the scene to fight the fire engulfing the factory. JOHANNESBURG - Booysens Informal settlement, in the south of Johannesburg, is currently on fire. Firefighters are battling to put out the blaze that's sweeping through the shacks. It's understood the fire is affecting many structures. The cause of the fire is not yet known. The Johannesburg Emergency Management Services is working on putting out the blaze. READ: Five dead in India vaccine plant fire, COVID drug unaffected Meanwhile, another fire broke out at the New World Industries warehouse in Wynberg in Sandton. It is also not clear what kindled the fire. Firefighters and emergency services are on the scene to fight the fire engulfing the factory.